      "sc:description": "PDBrestore is a web interface and command-line application for repairing raw PDB files used in molecular dynamics simulations. It adds hydrogen atoms, completes side chains, fills gaps, and generates simulation boxes, streamlining the preparatory work for drug design projects.",
